{"tid":419170,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先廢老沖閘失敗，想同我隻揪","createTime":"2017-09-30T08:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T18:09:35.000Z","uid":22005,"like":1297,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c5b889b84df6d4a363781a0e19b66e18458b2a","tid":419170,"uid":22005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"係深水埗背對住閘門<br />\n係關門果陣突然feel到有人推我背隻<br />\n我一望見到個廢老夾住左係中間<br />\n我即刻笑佢：「抵撚你死啦衝門 ,夾起中間」<br />\n佢個廢老fd即刻想拉我出去想同我隻揪<br />\n我即刻勁大力握住佢手臂<br />\n個廢老痛就縮手 咁岩度門就關埋左<br />\n<br />\n如果係你會點做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢出去打過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多一事不如少一事 算啦<br />\n<br />\n我好想出去打柒佢但度門關左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929ae502e9a8605b0d4c5aa33e4489f3cce7a9e4","tid":419170,"uid":86893,"like":216,"dislike":3,"score":213,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網隻抽"},{"pid":"7737c94527c2e6f8f4d3ff329180ea4ed8c6369f","tid":419170,"uid":22005,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"D廢老真係仆街黎 推完我仲覺得自己無錯"},{"pid":"382fc1a6a26f21a5319fe95bc7196f17382cd60e","tid":419170,"uid":22005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網隻抽</blockquote><br />\n大力握住佢果外已經當開戰啦"},{"pid":"1e3e8f55ec98d44f139d0433701f5a65bdb695d8","tid":419170,"uid":24698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"你贏左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca91a0dc8ed7fadb4a75046df41d8549ca1906cc","tid":419170,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":88,"score":-86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"好威威喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7