br />\n我即刻勁大力握住佢手臂<br />\n個廢老痛就縮手 咁岩度門就關埋左<br />\n<br />\n如果係你會點做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢出去打過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多一事不如少一事 算啦<br />\n<br />\n我好想出去打柒佢但度門關左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沖你老母 識唔撚識字"},{"pid":"012317096999ae504d7e8a98d159fc8531790233","tid":419170,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"佢冇野輸 報警既話就蝕<br />\n始終有出手 陰d陰d撞開佢咪算"},{"pid":"6b4fb0e5343bb72962f311c17c03432e3537deb7","tid":419170,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"衝門係仆街，不過上咗車望都唔吓後面有冇人上車就企死係門口咪又係一鳩樣"},{"pid":"9ca4e5fec596937434c13611a910421b6276ae8c","tid":419170,"uid":22005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衝門係仆街，不過上咗車望都唔吓後面有冇人上車就企死係門口咪又係一鳩樣</blockquote><br />\n架車滿晒人點入人呀"},{"pid":"48aa812b8ab5c0d6c097a0a23a60000a01298a48","tid":419170,"uid":112053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"廢老推你個下已經要大叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撚</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀</span>"},{"pid":"20e2d00cdb27e2b3e986a5752fe8631d35d87254","tid":419170,"uid":22005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老推你個下已經要大叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撚</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呀</span></blockquote><br />\n一推我已經轉身屌鳩佢<br />\n成個傻鳩夾撚住真係心都涼"},{"pid":"c4e4d3e3889df85e8e6201ef53cad316c7f3ecd4","tid":419170,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"廢老爛命一條<br 